<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="down-adv">down <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /daʊn/    美 /daʊn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>向下；（坐、躺、倒）下；在下面</strong></h4>
<p>反 up </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sun went down.
太阳落山了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sit down.
坐下。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>（水平、数量等）下降；减弱；降低</strong></h4>
<p>反 up </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The wind went down.
风停了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The tide is down.
潮退了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(指地点或状态) 往下方；在下方：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go down to the south
南下</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go down from London to the country
从伦敦到乡下</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>（记）下；（写）下：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please write down your answers on the paper.
请将答案写在纸上。</p></div></div>